<h2 id=\"1-executive-summary\">1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>CVSS v4 7.3</strong></li>
<li><strong>ATTENTION</strong>: Exploitable from an adjacent network</li>
<li><strong>Vendor</strong>: Siemens</li>
<li><strong>Equipment</strong>: Siveillance Video Camera</li>
<li><strong>Vulnerability</strong>: Classic Buffer Overflow</li>
