<li><strong>Vulnerability</strong>: Improper Authentication</li>
</ul>
<h2 id=\"2-risk-evaluation\">2. RISK EVALUATION</h2>
<p>Successful exploitation of this vulnerability could allow an attacker to access clear text communication.</p>
<h2 id=\"3-technical-details\">3. TECHNICAL DETAILS</h2>
<h3 id=\"31-affected-products\">3.1 AFFECTED PRODUCTS</h3>
