<h2 id=\"2-risk-evaluation\">2. RISK EVALUATION</h2>
<p>Successful exploitation of this vulnerability could allow an attacker to send a specially crafted CIP message and cause a denial-of-service condition on the affected device.</p>
<h2 id=\"3-technical-details\">3. TECHNICAL DETAILS</h2>
<h3 id=\"31-affected-products\">3.1 AFFECTED PRODUCTS</h3>
<p>The following Rockwell Automation products are affected:</p>
