<h2 id=\"2-risk-evaluation\">2. RISK EVALUATION</h2>
<p>Successful exploitation of this vulnerability could allow an attacker to cause a denial-of-service condition.</p>
<h2 id=\"3-technical-details\">3. TECHNICAL DETAILS</h2>
