<p><a href=\"https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2024-45474\" target=\"_blank\">CVE-2024-45474</a> has been assigned to this vulnerability. A CVSS v3 base score of 7.8 has been calculated; the CVSS vector string is (<a href=\"https://www.first.org/cvss/calculator/3.1#CVSS:3.1/AV:L/AC:L/PR:N/UI:R/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:H\" target=\"_blank\">CVSS:3.1/AV:L/AC:L/PR:N/UI:R/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:H</a>).</p>
