") (pubDate nil "Thu, 10 Oct 24 12:00:00 +0000") (creator nil "CISA") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "/node/22378"))) ("Siemens Teamcenter Visualization and JT2Go" "<p>As of January 10, 2023, CISA will no longer be updating ICS security advisories for Siemens product vulnerabilities beyond the initial advisory. For the most up-to-date information on vulnerabilities in this advisory, please see <a class=\"ext\" href=\"https://new.siemens.com/global/en/products/services/cert.html#SecurityPublications\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://new.siemens.com/global/en/products/services/cert.html#securitypublications\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Siemens' ProductCERT Security Advisories (CERT Services | Services | Siemens Global).</a>&nbsp;</p>
