<h4 id=\"325-improper-restriction-of-operations-within-the-bounds-of-a-memory-buffer-cwe-119\"><strong>3.2.5 </strong><a href=\"https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/119.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>IMPROPER RESTRICTION OF OPERATIONS WITHIN THE BOUNDS OF A MEMORY BUFFER CWE-119</strong></a></h4>
