<h4 id=\"329-out-of-bounds-write-cwe-787\"><strong>3.2.9 </strong><a href=\"https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/787.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>OUT-OF-BOUNDS WRITE CWE-787</strong></a></h4>
